pick up butter knife from counter

put knife into green cup inside sink
pick up green cup from sink basin

high_descs: Turn right, move to face the tomato on the counter, left of the stove.
Pick up the smaller silver knife on the counter.

Put the knife in the green cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup with knife in the sink.
Turn around, bring the cup to the counter.
Put the cup with knife on the counter, in front of the spoon and plate.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the left of the room, on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife beside the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and move to the sink directly in front of you.
Put the butter knife into the green cup in the sink.
Pick up the green cup with the butter knife in it.
Turn around and move to the counter above the dishwasher.
Put the cup with the butter knife down onto the counter above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put the butter knife into a green cup and place the cup onto the counter.
